# Production build config (committed — this is the PUBLIC deployed Worker origin, not a secret).
# Vite auto-loads this for `vite build` (production mode). The client socket connects here over wss://.
# Local dev still uses .env.local (higher precedence for `vite dev`); this file only affects the build.
# If the server Worker is ever renamed/moved, update this URL and re-deploy the client.
VITE_WS_URL=wss://trash-game.denjossal.workers.dev
